The owner of Augusto, Julien, is super friendly and helpful. He takes pride in his ice creams and local Portuguese products. We loved his place. Go visit him next time you're in Lisbon. Tell him I sent you. #europeantour #lisbon #forkingood
This strawberry sorbet is RIDICULOUS. The owner said they were fresh berries this morning. #europeantour #lisbon #forkingood #besticecreamever
Oh, and they make home made, artisanal ice cream. It is easily in my Top 3 favorite ice creams in the world. #europeantour #lisbon #besticecreamever

The other day we were wandering around Lisbon looking for some wine, cheese, and olives when we stumbled upon this place. It is now my favorite place in Lisbon. P.S. The cheese in the bottom right might be my favorite cheese in the world now. #europeantou
This cheese filled bacalhau croquette was deep fried deliciousness. I can see why the Portuguese are down with the salt cod. #europeantour #lisbon #bacalhau #forkingood
